name: PhiNesse Makeup Brushes Cleanser 150ml
short_description: A professional  disinfectant makeup brush cleanser, that cleans and conditions brushes in one step. Keeps your beauty tools free from dirt and bacteria. Gentle formula  which instantly dissolves any makeup on the brush and dries quickly, designed to extend the life of makeup brushes.
